sys-scan-graph (5.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major version 5.0.0 release with Intelligence Layer integration
  * Added AI-powered threat analysis and risk assessment
  * Added graph-based attack path modeling
  * Added automated rule generation and refinement
  * Added advanced anomaly detection with LLM integration
  * Added comprehensive reporting and visualization capabilities
  * Enhanced security hardening with capability dropping and seccomp
  * Added provenance metadata and supply-chain auditability
  * Added GPG signing support for detached signatures
  * Added NDJSON and SARIF output formats
  * Added reproducibility and determinism features
  * Updated JSON Schema to v2 with emitted metrics
  * Added fuzz testing harness and sanitizer support
  * Improved CI/CD pipeline with comprehensive testing
  * Updated documentation and contributing guidelines

 -- Joseph Mazzini <joseph@mazzlabs.works>  Mon, 25 Aug 2025 14:30:00 +0000

